      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain delivers power through a perfectly calibrated M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, including documented preventative subframe reinforcement and fresh RTABs, ensuring the structural integrity is superior to factory standards. The suspension geometry remains precise with no bushing play, and the hydraulic steering provides the unfiltered feedback coveted by purists. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically transparent, turn-key icon with no deferred maintenance.",
